Ilib NEWS -- user-visible changes between releases.
See ChangeLog for the full, detailed history.

1.1.10
  * Fix for newer versions of libpng that caused a compiler error.
  * Build, documentation, and repository modernization (in progress).

1.1.9
  * Added IFloodFill().

1.1.8
  * The Perl module is now bundled with the main distribution.
  * Fixed a bug in ICopyImageScaled().
  * libjpeg no longer calls exit() on input errors; an error code is
    returned instead.

Older releases: see ChangeLog.
